  "instructions": [
    "Peel and dice the potatoes into small cubes.",
    "In a large pot, sauté diced onions in butter until translucent.",
    "Add the potato cubes to the pot, stir, then pour in vegetable broth and maple syrup. Bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce heat to low, cover, and simmer for 20 minutes until potatoes are tender.",
    "Stir in fermented cabbage juice (if using) and heavy cream. Simmer for another 10 minutes.",
    "Season with salt and pepper to taste. Stir in fresh chives just before serving."
